import React, { useEffect, useRef } from "react"; import { gsap } from "gsap"; import { ScrollTrigger } from "gsap/ScrollTrigger"; import { MapIcon, ChartBarIcon, UserGroupIcon, ClockIcon, ShieldCheckIcon, ExclamationTriangleIcon, } from "@heroicons/react/24/outline"; import { useEmergency } from "../context/EmergencyContext"; const EmergencyDashboard = () => { const { emergencyHistory, location } = useEmergency(); const dashboardRef = useRef(null); useEffect(() => { gsap.registerPlugin(ScrollTrigger); // Animate dashboard elements on scroll const elements = dashboardRef.current.querySelectorAll(".dashboard-card"); elements.forEach((element, index) => { gsap.from(element, { opacity: 0, y: 50, duration: 0.8, delay: index * 0.2, scrollTrigger: { trigger: element, start: "top 80%", toggleActions: "play none none reverse", }, }); }); }, []); return (
